room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Key Quest in Spokane
review: Just AWESOME!! The games are so fun, the staff is so friendly. Great way to make friends, and friendly competition. I always have a great time there. üëçüëç

room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Key Quest in Spokane
review: Recently attended with son's and grandson's - my son's had all been here several time over the years, this was my first visit. I thought the staff was great, the attraction was great, everything worked as it was supposed to. It was safe. It was fair. All in all a great place to spend a COLD evening!

room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Key Quest in Spokane
review: Took the family and extended family here for a birthday party. The staff working made the experience memorable and exciting. They had lots of energy and made everybody laugh. The arena is large with multiple levels quick made it fun. I recommend to anybody considering it.
